          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/astro_match_start_astro_mirage_convo03_01.mp3",
          "text": "You like working for Nashala?",
          "duration": 1.933
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Mirage",
          "audioFile": "mirage_match_start_astro_mirage_convo03_02",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/mirage_match_start_astro_mirage_convo03_02.mp3",
          "text": "I do.  When she's free of her vessel, she offers scintilating conversation.  When she rests, I get to go bowling.",
          "duration": 8.732
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Holliday",
          "audioFile": "astro_match_start_astro_mirage_convo03_03",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/astro_match_start_astro_mirage_convo03_03.mp3",
          "text": "Bowling?",
          "duration": 1.083
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Mirage",
          "audioFile": "mirage_match_start_astro_mirage_convo03_04",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/mirage_match_start_astro_mirage_convo03_04.mp3",
          "text": "I learned about it in England.  It is the sport of kings.",
          "duration": 3.807
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "grey talon_holliday_convo01",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Grey talon",
          "audioFile": "orion_match_start_astro_orion_convo01_01",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/orion_match_start_astro_orion_convo01_01.mp3",
          "text": "What do you want from The Patron?",
          "duration": 1.543
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Holliday",
          "audioFile": "astro_match_start_astro_orion_convo01_02",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/astro_match_start_astro_orion_convo01_02.mp3",
          "text": "Revenge.",
          "duration": 1.253
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Grey talon",
          "audioFile": "orion_match_start_astro_orion_convo01_03",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/orion_match_start_astro_orion_convo01_03.mp3",
          "text": "Looks like we have something in common.",
          "duration": 1.789
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "conversationId": "grey talon_holliday_convo02",
      "lines": [
        {
          "order": 1,
          "character": "Grey talon",
          "audioFile": "orion_match_start_astro_orion_convo02_01",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/orion_match_start_astro_orion_convo02_01.mp3",
          "text": "Can I give you an unsolicted word of adivce Holliday?",
          "duration": 2.686
        },
        {
          "order": 2,
          "character": "Holliday",
          "audioFile": "astro_match_start_astro_orion_convo02_02",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/astro_match_start_astro_orion_convo02_02.mp3",
          "text": "Why not.",
          "duration": 1.318
        },
        {
          "order": 3,
          "character": "Grey talon",
          "audioFile": "orion_match_start_astro_orion_convo02_03",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/orion_match_start_astro_orion_convo02_03.mp3",
          "text": "People are going to tell you that there is a difference between justice and revenge, that you will dishonor the dead by stooping to their killer's level\u2026ignore them. Revenge isn't for the dead.  It's for the living.",
          "duration": 14.323
        },
        {
          "order": 4,
          "character": "Holliday",
          "audioFile": "astro_match_start_astro_orion_convo02_04",
          "audioUrl": "https://deadlock.vlviewer.com/Games/Deadlock/DeadlockJan2026/Audio/astro_match_start_astro_orion_convo02_04.mp3",
          "text": "I knew I liked you.",
          "duration": 1.565
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}